OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly heavy or thundery showers
OL,6,Fwill soon clear eastwards to leave
OL,7,Fanother dry day with plenty of
OL,8,Fsunshine and hot temperatures. Light
OL,9,Fwinds will offer little relief though
OL,10,Fa gentle sea breeze may develop close
OL,11,Fto the coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA dry, mostly clear but humid
OL,14,Fnight is expected with light winds.
OL,15,FSome patchy mist may form inland and
OL,16,Falong the coast.
OL,17,
OL,18,CWednesday:FDry with long sunny periods
OL,19,Fand light winds. Widely very warm or
OL,20,Fhot with heatwave conditions expected,
OL,21,Fincluding overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
