OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FTemperatures climbing further,
OL,7,Fpotentially becoming very hot by day,
OL,8,Fwith very warm intervening nights.
OL,9,FMainly fine with further sunshine,
OL,10,Fhowever this perhaps eventually
OL,11,Ftriggering thunderstorms during Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
